nie ste pekný chlap ale idiot.

164
00:14:27,850 --> 00:14:30,470
Alebo ste pokrytec?

165
00:14:36,890 --> 00:14:38,930
Spamätajte sa, Joon Ha.

166
00:14:38,930 --> 00:14:42,740
Kang Ma Roo nie je niekto, 
komu by ste mal pomáhať, 
ale niekto, koho sa treba zbaviť.

167
00:14:42,990 --> 00:14:44,850
Ak naozaj chcete mať Seo Eun Gi ...

168
00:14:44,850 --> 00:14:46,840
Musím ju mať?

169
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:47,750
Čože?

170
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:50,000
Ak niekoho milujem,

171
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,210
znamená to, že ho musím mať?

172
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:57,410
To si nemyslím.

173
00:15:00,300 --> 00:15:02,890
Idiot.

174
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:08,410
Nemyslím si, že sa líšime.

175
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:12,900
Sme na rovnakej ceste,

176
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:16,280
len vy ste stretol Han Jae Hee,

177
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:19,120
a ja som stretol Seo Eun Gi.

178
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:22,980
Aby sme sa už viac nestretli,

179
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:28,800
pôjdem celkom inou cestou.

180
00:15:32,540 --> 00:15:36,190
V budúcnosti, keď uplynie čas...

181
00:15:36,310 --> 00:15:38,930
a budeme mať pocit, ako keby to, 
čo sme chceli

182
00:15:39,170 --> 00:15:42,780
vlastne nič nebolo,

183
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:45,680
tiež sa stretneme...

184
00:15:46,610 --> 00:15:49,440
na tej istej ceste?

185
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:52,660
Sunbaenim?

186
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:57,630
Áno, prokurátor Choi.

187
00:15:57,950 --> 00:16:00,700
