189
00:16:03,590 --> 00:16:10,160
Náš právnik, pred hodinou 
ztiahol žalobu proti Kang Ma Roo-ovi.

190
00:16:12,910 --> 00:16:14,540
Čože?

191
00:16:14,540 --> 00:16:16,630
Čo to hovoríte?

192
00:16:18,180 --> 00:16:23,080
Kang Ma Roo sa dobrovoľne objavil 
na polícii a požiadal o vyšetrovanie?

193
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:28,510
Prečo?

194
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:31,160
