To ... naozaj neviem.

481
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:47,450
A...

482
00:40:47,450 --> 00:40:48,770
Ale...

483
00:40:48,770 --> 00:40:54,970
Ja som na niečo - na niekoho...
Za niekým som sa hnala.

484
00:40:54,970 --> 00:40:57,340
Kto to bol?

485
00:40:57,340 --> 00:41:00,860
Nie som si istá. Nevidela som ho.

486
00:41:00,860 --> 00:41:03,110
A....

487
