510
00:42:39,290 --> 00:42:42,090
Len tak ma to napadlo.

511
00:43:51,220 --> 00:43:52,420
Ma Roo.

512
00:43:52,420 --> 00:43:53,850
<i>Deje sa tam niečo neobvyklé?</i>

