514
00:43:57,640 --> 00:43:59,280
Nepôjdeme na rande?

515
00:44:00,190 --> 00:44:01,300
Mimochodom,

516
00:44:01,300 --> 00:44:04,690
pred našim domom stojí Han Jae Hee. 

517
00:44:05,470 --> 00:44:06,560
Neotváraj dvere.

518
00:44:06,560 --> 00:44:10,530
Neotváraj dvere, kým neprídem. 
Hneď som tam.

519
00:44:23,190 --> 00:44:24,530
Eun Gi.

520
00:44:24,530 --> 00:44:26,080
Seo Eun Gi.

521
00:44:26,930 --> 00:44:29,800
Eun Gi, si doma?

522
00:45:04,700 --> 00:45:09,530
Vieš aká som bola naštvaná, 
