524
00:45:17,600 --> 00:45:18,350
Vážne.

525
00:45:20,420 --> 00:45:22,950
Je mi to ľúto. Nabudúce budem opatrná.

526
00:45:24,220 --> 00:45:24,740
Áno.

527
00:45:25,050 --> 00:45:28,820
Priniesla som ti jedlo, ktoré máš rada.

528
00:45:33,080 --> 00:45:34,370
Ďakujem.

529
00:45:44,760 --> 00:45:46,100
Nikto nie je doma?

530
00:45:47,260 --> 00:45:49,850
A čo Čoko a Jae Gil?

531
00:45:52,280 --> 00:45:54,320
Čoko a Jae Gil....

532
